# UI Kit

All shared UI components live in `lib/core/ui/`. Never use raw Flutter primitives (e.g. `Text`, `ElevatedButton`, `showModalBottomSheet`) directly in feature code — always go through the UI kit.

## Project Structure

```
lib/
  core/
    ui/
      _theme.dart                ← DesignTokens + ThemeData extension + AppThemes light/dark
      text.dart                  ← UIKText semantic text widget
      loading_state_mixin.dart   ← LoadingStateMixin for async widgets
      buttons/
        base_button.dart         ← AppButton stateful widget (enum-driven)
        ui_kit_button.dart       ← UIKButton fluent facade
      bottom_sheet/
        ui_kit_bottom_sheet.dart ← UIKBottomSheet static facade (if present)
        bottom_sheet_shell.dart  ← shell: header + auto-scroll body + footer
        bottom_sheet_action.dart ← BottomSheetAction model
        bottom_sheet_close_button.dart
        gradient_fade.dart       ← theme-aware gradient overlay
      hero_dialog/
        hero_dialog_route.dart
        custom_rect_tween.dart
        popup_card_tile.dart
        popup_card_content.dart
```

