## Tokens & Theme

All raw values are in `DesignTokens`. Never hardcode colors, font sizes, radii, or shadows — reference the token instead.

```dart
// ✅
color: DesignTokens.primary
borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(DesignTokens.buttonBorderRadius)

// ❌
color: Color(0xFF6FCF97)
borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(14)
```

Access themed styles via the `ThemeData` extension inside widgets:

```dart
final theme = Theme.of(context);
theme.h3Style        // heading
theme.bodyStyle      // body
theme.buttonLargeStyle
```

