## LoadingStateMixin

Used internally by `AppButton`. Available for any `StatefulWidget` that needs async loading state.

```dart
class _MyWidgetState extends State<MyWidget> with LoadingStateMixin {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return ValueListenableBuilder<bool>(
      valueListenable: isLoading,
      builder: (context, loading, _) {
        return AppButton(
          label: 'Go',
          onTap: () => withLoading(myAsyncFn),
          isLoading: loading,
          type: ButtonType.primary,
        );
      },
    );
  }
}
```

`withLoading` automatically sets loading state, runs the callback, fires `HapticFeedback.heavyImpact()` on success, and resets loading in `finally`.

