## Adding New Components

When adding a new component to the UI kit:

1. Create the raw widget in `lib/core/ui/<component>/app_<component>.dart`
2. If it has variants, use enums — never string flags
3. Create a fluent facade `ui_kit_<component>.dart` if it has multiple call patterns
4. Always pull colors from `Theme.of(context)` — never hardcode
5. Update this file
